  "descriptions": [
    {
      "text": "The game puts the player into the role of Princess Elise, a young, spoiled princess on a quest to impress a handsome adventurer into being her boyfriend.\n\nPrincess Elise has a unique ability to pout, changing the game's landscape or enemy behavior. This ability can be used to force enemies to drop more loot, make the game easier or even complete sidequests.",
